        {
            "title": "萬科首次尋求人民幣債券展期 中國房地產危機再現深化跡象",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 陷入困境的中國開發商萬科首次提議將人民幣債券展期，成為這場動搖中國金融市場的房地產危機進一步深化的最新跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周三晚發布的公告，這家開發商尋求將12月15日到期的20億元人民幣債券展期。萬科將於12月10日召開持有人會議，討論展期相關事項。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Builder Vanke Seeks Extension on Yuan Bond for First Time</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%91%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%86%8D%E7%8F%BE%E6%B7%B1%E5%8C%96%E8%B7%A1%E8%B1%A1-141935772.html",
